{"tid":624040,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] 人中之龍極2 / 人中系列 討論區9","createTime":"2018-04-10T13:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T16:11:50.000Z","uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b628862afac5920187a3acd8ee3b9d40796e3b01","tid":624040,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:00:50.000Z","msg":"除咗極2之外 其他都可以問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <del>(有冇人答就唔知)</del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1cBxq1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1cBxq1v.jpg&h=cda0c423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">人龍極2故事背景:</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事主要圍繞多年前原作「人中之龍2」桐生一馬所屬的東城會，同關西幫會近江連合旗下鄉龍會「關西之龍」鄉田龍司作出全面對決: 關東 vs 關西<br />\n<br />\n《極2》故事的骨幹跟隨原作之外，在本作中會加入真島吾朗的新故事，主題是「真島吾朗的真相」。<br />\n 追加故事劇情將敘述初代作品《人中之龍》與《人中之龍 2》之間所發生的故事。<br />\n<br />\n《人中之龍 2》的真島，因「某事件」而離開東城會。<br />\n在本次追加的故事劇情中，將公開這尚未解開的謎團。此外，在這追加故事劇情中，真島吾朗將變為可操作角色。<br />\n另外真島更會自人龍0以來，首次再度回到蒼天堀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/axRXah9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaxRXah9.jpg&h=3a03d268&s={SIZE}\" />[/center]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IYa8s7n4sOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIYa8s7n4sOQ&d=%2FR2c0YqBzdZlJdC6XAdWm8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=568d0ead\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IYa8s7n4sOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人中之龍極2 討論區 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/491655/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/491655/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n人中之龍極2 討論區(3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/494140/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/494140/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n［我愛風化島］人中之龍極2 討論區 3<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/497266/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/497266/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[ 差婆 風化島 龍友 ] 人中之龍極2 討論區 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/499974/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/499974/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[ 差婆 雪紀 橋本梨菜 ] 人中之龍極2 討論區 6<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/504069/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/504069/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[ 今晚打老虎 ] 人中之龍極2 討論區 7<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/509565/page/39?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/509565/page/39?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n人中之龍極2 討論區 8<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/516449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/516449/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e88df14494484b5a1ab421eb5cab6b678e5de6e1","tid":624040,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"BGM<br />\n遊戲內歌SiM &ndash; A @ The Sound Of Breath 2首(搞到冇咗ending聖詩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n風化島幫女仔整衫 &ndash; As you like  SEGA/吉田 沙織/美緒(Castledoor)<br />\n最終BOSS戰 - 散るは永遠の刹那<br />\n<br />\n極2 OST為限定版先有,出面都搵唔到(電子下載版)<br />\n<br />\n鍾意啲歌不防支持正版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (人中0有部份BGM都有)<br />\n日本AMAZON(只有MP3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E9%BE%8D%E3%81%8C%E5%A6%82%E3%81%8F0-%E8%AA%93%E3%81%84%E3%81%AE%E5%A0%B4%E6%89%80-%E3%82%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%82%B8%E3%83%8A%E3%83%AB%E3%82%B5%E3%82%A6%E3%83%B3%E3%83%89%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF-Side-SEGA/dp/B00UB63E0Q/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1523364469&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=%E9%BE%8D%E3%81%8C%E5%A6%82%E3%81%8F0+OST\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E3%2581%258C%25E5%25A6%2582%25E3%2581%258F0-%25E8%25AA%2593%25E3%2581%2584%25E3%2581%25AE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2589%2580-%25E3%2582%25AA%25E3%2583%25AA%25E3%2582%25B8%25E3%2583%258A%25E3%2583%25AB%25E3%2582%25B5%25E3%2582%25A6%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2583%2589%25E3%2583%2588%25E3%2583%